22/11/2005
IVAILOVGRAD, Bulgaria -- A new Bulgarian-Greek border checkpoint, Ivailovgrad-Kyprinos, will become operational by the summer of 2006.
The announcement Monday (21 November) followed a meeting among local authorities from the Bulgarian district of Haskovo and the Greek prefecture Evros.
They met in the border town of Ivailovgrad to discuss preparations.
(BNR, MPA - 21/11/05)
